import React from 'react';

const Form = ({submitFn}) => {
    <form
        onSubmit={submitFn}>
        <imput 
            name="name"
            placeholder="name"
        />
        <imput 
            name="link"
            placeholder="link"
        />
        <imput 
            name="image"
            placeholder="image"></imput>
        <textarea 
            name="description"
            placeholder="description"
        />
        <button>addItem</button>
    </form>
}

export default Form;
